OL,3,CFire breaks out on moor
OL,5,FA large fire has broken out on
OL,6,FSaddleworth Moor near Greenfield in
OL,7,FOldham.
OL,9,FGreater Manchester Fire and Rescue has
OL,10,Fasked people to avoid the area while
OL,11,Fits crews tackle the blaze.
OL,13,FIt posted on X: "Residents are advised
OL,14,Fto keep doors and windows closed."
OL,16,FThe fire is burning near Pots and Pans
OL,17,FMonument, a war memorial obelisk on
OL,18,FAlderman's Hill.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/3
