OL,3,CFire breaks out on moor
OL,5,FTwo other moorland fires have also
OL,6,Fbroken out on Marsden Moors in West
OL,7,FYorkshire.
OL,9,FWest Yorkshire Fire and Rescue said it
OL,10,Fhas 10 crews at the scene, including
OL,11,Fspecialist wildfire teams.
OL,13,FIt posted on Facebook: "We are
OL,14,Fcurrently attending two moorland fires
OL,15,Fat Deer Hill and the Five Mile Post
OL,16,Farea.
OL,18,F"We are asking all members of the
OL,19,Fpublic to avoid the area. Anyone
OL,20,Fcurrently on the moors is advised to
OL,21,Fleave the area as soon as possible.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/3
