OL,3,CFire breaks out on moor
OL,5,F"Road closures are expected in
OL,6,Fsurrounding areas whilst crews from
OL,7,Facross West Yorkshire respond to this
OL,8,Fwildfire."
OL,10,FThe A62 Manchester Road in Marsden is
OL,11,Fblocked in both directions between
OL,12,FMount Road and Huddersfield Road.
